@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam participantBackgroundColor Yellow
skinparam participantBorderColor #B8860B
skinparam actorBackgroundColor Yellow
skinparam actorBorderColor #B8860B
skinparam boundaryBackgroundColor Yellow
skinparam boundaryBorderColor #B8860B
skinparam controlBackgroundColor Yellow
skinparam controlBorderColor #B8860B
skinparam entityBackgroundColor Yellow
skinparam entityBorderColor #B8860B
skinparam databaseBackgroundColor Yellow
skinparam databaseBorderColor #B8860B
skinparam lifelineStrategy solid
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

actor "Khach hang\n(Customer)" as User #Yellow
boundary "ContactPage\n(Public Form)" as UI #Yellow
boundary "contactService" as APIClient #Yellow
boundary "api.ts\n(Axios)" as Axios #Yellow
control "ContactController" as Ctrl #Yellow
control "ContactService" as Svc #Yellow
entity "UnitOfWork" as UoW #Yellow
database "GenericRepository\nContactMessage" as Repo #Yellow
database "PostgreSQL\n(PMC_Tour)" as DB #Yellow

== Submit lien he (POST /api/Contact - Public) ==

User -> UI : 1: Mo trang Contact (/contact)
activate UI

UI -> UI : 1.1: Render trang
note right: Giao dien gom:\n- Navbar (shared)\n- Hero section (gradient primary)\n- Form contact (2 cot)\n- Thong tin lien he\n- Ban do

UI --> User : 1.1.1: Hien thi form: Name, Email, Subject (dropdown), Message

User -> UI : 2: Dien form va nhan "Send Message"
activate UI

UI -> UI : 2.1: Validate frontend (required fields)
alt [2.2] Thieu thong tin
    UI --> User : 2.2.1: Browser bao loi required
else [2.3] Du thong tin
    UI -> UI : 2.3.1: Set isSubmitting = true
    UI -> UI : 2.3.2: Hien thi spinner "Sending..."

    UI -> APIClient : 2.3.3: contactService.create({ name, email, subject, message })
    activate APIClient

    APIClient -> Axios : 2.3.4: api.post('/Contact', formData)
    activate Axios
    note right: Endpoint public -\nkhong can JWT token

    Axios -> Ctrl : 2.3.5: HTTP POST /api/Contact
    activate Ctrl
    note right: Khong co [Authorize] -\nbat ky ai cung co the gui

    Ctrl -> Svc : 2.3.6: CreateAsync(createContactRequest)
    activate Svc

    Svc -> Svc : 2.3.6.1: AutoMapper.Map<CreateContactRequest -> ContactMessage>
    note right: Map: Name, Email, Subject, Message

    Svc -> Svc : 2.3.6.2: Set CreatedAt = DateTime.UtcNow

    Svc -> UoW : 2.3.6.3: ContactMessages.AddAsync(contact)
    activate UoW
    UoW -> Repo : 2.3.6.3.1: AddAsync(ContactMessage)
    activate Repo
    Repo -> DB : 2.3.6.3.2: INSERT INTO ContactMessages\n(Name, Email, Subject, Message,\nIsRead=false, CreatedAt, IsDeleted=false)
    activate DB
    DB --> Repo : 2.3.6.3.3: Created
    deactivate DB
    deactivate Repo
    deactivate UoW

    Svc -> UoW : 2.3.7: SaveChangesAsync()
    activate UoW
    UoW -> DB : 2.3.7.1: COMMIT
    activate DB
    DB --> UoW : 2.3.7.2: success
    deactivate DB
    deactivate UoW

    Svc --> Ctrl : 2.3.8: ApiResponse<ContactResponse>("Message sent successfully")
    deactivate Svc

    Ctrl --> Axios : 2.3.9: HTTP 200 + JSON
    deactivate Ctrl

    Axios --> APIClient : 2.3.10: res.data
    deactivate Axios

    APIClient --> UI : 2.3.11: ApiResponse
    deactivate APIClient

    UI -> UI : 2.3.12: Set submitSuccess = true
    UI -> UI : 2.3.13: Reset form ve trang thai ban dau
    note right: setName = ''\nsetEmail = ''\nsetSubject = 'General Inquiry'\nsetMessage = ''

    UI --> User : 2.3.14: Hien thi "Message Sent!" + check icon
    note right: Sau 3 giay,\ntu dong reset submitSuccess
    deactivate UI
end

@enduml
